                  <div id="innerbodycontent" class="row nolayout"><div class="offset1 span10">
            <div id="sm-cog-elements" class="noprint"></div>
            <div class="allset-page-heading"><h1>Using "bei" sentences</h1></div>
            <!-- subtitle -->
            <div id="contentSub" ></div>
            <!-- /subtitle -->
                        <div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="mw-parser-output"><div id="ibox" class="toc">
	<div class="ibox-link"><span class="plainlinks"><a href="ASGHF9F1" class="mw-redirect" title="ASGHF9F1"><img src="https&#58;//resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/silk/link.png" /></a></span></div>
	<ul class="ibox-list">
               <li class="ibox-level-cefr-hsk clearfix">
                        
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><span style="font-size: 1.4em;"><a href="B1_grammar_points" title="B1 grammar points"> B1</a></span> / <span style="font-size:0.75em;"><a href="HSK3_grammar_points" class="mw-redirect" title="HSK3 grammar points">HSK3</a></span></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-level clearfix" style="display:none">
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="B1_grammar_points" title="B1 grammar points"> B1</a></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-level-hsk clearfix" style="display:none;">
			<div class="ibox-label">Level</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="HSK3_grammar_points" class="mw-redirect" title="HSK3 grammar points"> HSK3</a></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-similarto clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-similarto-hsk clearfix" style="display:none;">
			<div class="ibox-label">Similar to</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"></div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-usedfor clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Used for</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="Sentence_Patterns" title="Sentence Patterns">Sentence Patterns</a>, <a href="Expressing_passive_voice" title="Expressing passive voice">Expressing passive voice</a> </div>
		</li>
		<li class="ibox-keywords clearfix">
			<div class="ibox-label">Keywords</div>
			<div class="ibox-info"><a href="被" title="被">被</a></div>
		</li>
		
	</ul>
	<div class="ibox-image"><a href="./File:Chinese-grammar-wiki-bei4.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Chinese-grammar-wiki-bei4.jpg" src="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/3/3c/Chinese-grammar-wiki-bei4.jpg/300px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-bei4.jpg" decoding="async" width="300" height="300" srcset="https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/3/3c/Chinese-grammar-wiki-bei4.jpg/450px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-bei4.jpg 1.5x, https://resources.allsetlearning.com/gramwiki/images/thumb/3/3c/Chinese-grammar-wiki-bei4.jpg/600px-Chinese-grammar-wiki-bei4.jpg 2x" /></a></div>
</div> 
<p>被 (bèi) sentences, which are called 被字句 (bèizìjù) in Chinese, are a key way to express the <a href="Passive_voice" title="Passive voice">passive voice</a> in modern Mandarin Chinese.  In passive sentences, the <i>object</i> of an action becomes the subject of the sentence, and the "doer" of the action, which would have been the subject of the normal (active voice) sentence, becomes secondary and may or may not be mentioned in the passive sentence.
</p>
<div id="toc" class="toc"><input type="checkbox" role="button" id="toctogglecheckbox" class="toctogglecheckbox" style="display:none" /><div class="toctitle" lang="en" dir="ltr"><h2>Contents</h2><span class="toctogglespan"><label class="toctogglelabel" for="toctogglecheckbox"></label></span></div>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-1"><a href="Using_&quot;bei&quot;_sentences#What_is_a_.E8.A2.AB_sentence.3F"><span class="tocnumber">1</span> <span class="toctext">What is a 被 sentence?</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-2"><a href="Using_&quot;bei&quot;_sentences#Why_use_them.3F"><span class="tocnumber">2</span> <span class="toctext">Why use them?</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-1 tocsection-3"><a href="Using_&quot;bei&quot;_sentences#How_to_Use_.E8.A2.AB_Sentences"><span class="tocnumber">3</span> <span class="toctext">How to Use 被 Sentences</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-4"><a href="Using_&quot;bei&quot;_sentences#Structure"><span class="tocnumber">3.1</span> <span class="toctext">Structure</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-5"><a href="Using_&quot;bei&quot;_sentences#Examples"><span class="tocnumber">3.2</span> <span class="toctext">Examples</span></a></li>
